record_data.record_plain_text:
PARKWAY GENERATION OPERATING LLC Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service Parkway Generation Operating LLC ("Parkway Gen Operating") provides Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service ("Reactive Supply Service") from various generating facilities to the PJM Interconnection, L.L.C. ("PJM") system. This Rate Schedule for the Essex 9 generating facility located in Newark, New Jersey sets forth Parkway Gen Operating's revenue requirement for the provision of Reactive Service from the facility pursuant to Schedule 2 of the PJM Open Access Transmission Tariff, which provides for PJM to pay generation owners their monthly revenue requirements for Reactive Service.
This Rate Schedule shall be effective upon the date authorized by the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission.
REVENUE REQUIREMENT Total Annual Revenue Requirement is $1,034,992. Total Monthly Revenue Requirement is $86,249.
